'''Evren Eren Elmalı''' (born 7 July 2000) is a Turkish professional [[Association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[Defender (association football)#Full-back|left-back]] for [[Süper Lig]] club [[Galatasaray S.K. (football)|Galatasaray]] and the [[Turkey national football team|Turkey national team]].

==Professional career==

===Kasımpaşa===
Elmalı is a youth product of [[Kartal S.K.|Kartalspor]] and [[Kasımpaşa S.K.|Kasımpaşa]], signing his first professional contract with the latter in 2019.

====Silivrispor (loan)====
He began his senior career on loan with [[Silivrispor]] in the [[TFF First League]] for the 2019-20 season.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.fanatik.com.tr/eren-elmali-kimdir-kac-yasinda-eren-elmali-nereli-ve-hangi-takimlarda-oynadi-2263582|title=Eren Elmalı kimdir, kaç yaşında? Eren Elmalı nereli ve hangi...|website=Fanatik}}</ref>

====Return to Kasımpaşa====
He returned to Kasımpaşa for the 2020-21 season. He made his professional debut with Kasımpaşa in a 2-1 [[Süper Lig]] win over [[Alanyaspor]] on 11 January 2021.<ref name="Soccerway 2021">{{cite web | title=Alanyaspor vs. Kasımpaşa - 11 January 2021 | website=Soccerway | date=11 Jan 2021 | url=https://uk.soccerway.com/matches/2021/01/11/turkey/super-lig/alanyaspor/kasimpasa-sk/3352937/ | access-date=15 Jan 2021}}</ref>

===Trabzonspor===
On 17 July 2022, Elmalı transferred to [[Trabzonspor]] on a 3-year contract.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.fotomac.com.tr/trabzonspor/2022/06/17/trabzonspor-eren-elmali-dogucan-haspolat-ve-jens-stryger-larsen-transferlerinin-maliyetini-acikladi|title=Trabzonspor Eren Elmalı Doğucan Haspolat ve Jens Stryger Larsen transferlerinin maliyetini açıkladı!|website=Fotomaç}}</ref>

===Galatasaray===
On 11 February 2025, he signed a three-and-a-half-year contract with [[Galatasaray S.K. (football)|Galatasaray]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.galatasaray.org/haber/gs-sportif-a-s/eren-elmali-galatasarayda/57224|title=Eren Elmalı Galatasaray'da!|publisher=Galatasaray S.K.|date=11 February 2025|access-date=11 February 2025}}</ref>

On 13 November 2025, Elmalı was banned from playing for 45 days for his involvement in the [[2025 Turkish football betting scandal]].<ref>{{cite web|publisher=Haberler|url=https://en.haberler.com/here-is-the-penalty-for-102-football-players-who-19250345/|title=Here is the penalty for 102 football players who placed bets! Two stars from Galatasaray are also on the list.|date=13 November 2025|access-date=25 November 2025}}</ref>

==International career==
Elmalı was called up to the senior [[Turkey national football team|Turkey national team]] for [[UEFA Nations League]] matches in June 2022.<ref name="tff.org">{{cite web | title=A Millî Takım'ın UEFA Uluslar Ligi maçlarının aday kadrosu açıklandı - A Milli Takım Haber Detayları TFF | website=tff.org | url=https://www.tff.org/default.aspx?pageID=202&ftxtID=37727 | language=tr | access-date=June 2, 2022}}</ref>

